{"tid":931800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"J奶女優海外初體驗留台灣 老街公然開腿兼自摸","createTime":"2018-12-07T09:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T10:55:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b4d2faba245313c2c78f3ce86deef2fcc17433","tid":931800,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/12/07/2635565_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F2635565_1.jpg&h=a88a60e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有最強body的J罩杯女優JULIA 近日獻出台灣初體驗，登上JKF雜誌12月號封面女郎。這次特別選在充滿台灣風味的小旅館取景，她表示，「拍攝之前就一直很好奇JKF雜誌的拍攝會是怎麼進行，結果是出乎意料的開心與新奇。這也是我第一次到海外進行雜誌拍攝，難得感到有些緊張，腦海裡一直思考該怎麼做才能更好，希望成品粉絲喜歡。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/12/07/2635565_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F2635565_2.jpg&h=26056704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/12/07/2635565_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F2635565_3.jpg&h=eaaf679a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被問到喜歡的男生類型，JULIA：「根據以往的交往經驗來看的話，我喜歡有工作的男生，積極上進，努力不放棄的人是我最欣賞的類型。目前我比較喜歡貓系男子呢！雖然百依百順會讓我覺得被重視疼愛，但是久了會覺得這個男生好像沒有了自己的個性，所以不如捉摸不定非常神祕的貓系男子，而且感覺很新鮮有趣呢。」"},{"pid":"47ed8c9e005f6102eb82fc685e8b7760e6a6b391","tid":931800,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b29c0f1d1d207453ce58a7e12170a22a022d50d4","tid":931800,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">老</span>"},{"pid":"cf94dd90f571bbe56506c74b6f1255e7768c0680","tid":931800,"uid":66514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"變性人樣子"},{"pid":"7a36b817e1ae72477b82b6c700df9b3f7645a4fa","tid":931800,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c301d0cc216b006b8066272d60ee150856759","tid":931800,"uid":3177,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_bg_Hymvk0iM/SS5vkyloHwI/AAAAAAAAA0c/JEghHeWoQA8/s400/銀河鐵道+999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F_bg_Hymvk0iM%2FSS5vkyloHwI%2FAAAAAAAAA0c%2FJEghHeWoQA8%2Fs400%2F%E9%8A%80%E6%B2%B3%E9%90%B5%E9%81%93%2B999.jpg&h=e8d2ca4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57050054cc61ace4b62c963718ef0f63d9fcf08a","tid":931800,"uid":59163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:08:20.000Z","msg":"後面呀婆個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05b4f4db4b51b32faa2bf490587dd07f8de26e4","tid":931800,"uid":86272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯老公開腿兼自摸"},{"pid":"6e974373aebf7c399c13bb8d9fbcdac54b929bf7","tid":931800,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"我喜歡有工作的男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ne個都係條件?..."},{"pid":"c9fed16f06c09fedf0afaf46517a17853304409c","tid":931800,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e974373aebf7c399c13bb8d9fbcdac54b929bf7","tid":931800,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"我喜歡有工作的男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s